name: One morning in the bathroom
description:
My version of I believe in 6 impossible things before breakfast (a reference to Alice in Wonderland movie 2010)

Trying to make mundane little daily life an extraordinary experience to make it less boring and actually enjoying it. Nowadays I am trying to make a good thing into a routine then into a habit. It’s not easy at first, especially in the morning. So I’m trying to make it more interesting than it actually is.  

One morning in the bathroom (2020)
4000x4000 px

This first NFT to you by NZAKIRA. Hope you like it!
